{"tid":1352453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再理啲風向撚，去元朗絕對係主線任","createTime":"2019-07-22T19:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T18:52:40.000Z","uid":196430,"like":102,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"252800cf9a5e1eeb912c4c21444a167829994156","tid":1352453,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:10:53.000Z","msg":"突然好多人吹風話唔好去元朗，話會失焦，話會spin，話會分化&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我屌哂你老母呀﹗</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解上一輩嘅人咁怕老共？去到今時今日都仲會講唔好得罪共產黨？就係因為六四屠城嘅傷痕，深深刻印在喺上一輩嘅抗爭者心入面﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢哋怕行動升級，怕勇武，怕自己爭取嘅嘢，只敢喺「遊行」呢個安全區度原地踏步，導致香港三十年民主運動原地踏步﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恐懼就係極權政府統治嘅最終兵器﹗</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家港共政權用黑社會發動恐怖襲擊，試圖打擊香港逆權運動，目的唔係咩以民鬥民，而係同屠城一樣，要你驚﹗要你恐懼﹗要你懷念以前虛偽嘅和平，更加要你以後一切示威活動，都要蒙上721恐襲嘅陰霾，從此自我設限﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經有人中咗計，咩元朗我哋唔熟，嗰班人喪，會有人死&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你今日開始考慮呢啲嘢，以後你嘅一切行動都唔會再向前行，唔會再升級，唔會再進化﹗而呢樣正正就係中共最想你做嘅嘢﹗<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所謂最應該恐懼嘅嘢，就係恐懼本身﹗</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我哋今個星期入元朗，唔係要打交，唔係要尋仇，而係我哋都要同港共政權、同自己、同全香港人講&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果呢個世界係誰大誰惡誰正確，而家就係香港人最大最惡﹗</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港共政權已經撕開一切偽裝，露出警黑政三位一體嘅本質，呢個就係佢最脆弱嘅時候，因為以恐懼管治係一場政治豪賭，而且主動權全不在管理一方，只要人民唔怕，我哋打爆埋佢呢一張牌，佢就全盤皆輸﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港、時代革命﹗</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b2655cdad28cc4cd5a9faa2d983754d32fb274de","tid":1352453,"uid":1544,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"一句講晒 <br />\n唔嚟元朗 以後唔駛旨意屯元天人出港島"},{"pid":"16085553a3be2923a767928090013be057e42d9b","tid":1352453,"uid":180429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:11:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d655791926feac08330629f592582fc654eacdb0","tid":1352453,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2655cdad28cc4cd5a9faa2d983754d32fb274de","tid":1352453,"uid":1544,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"一句講晒 <br />\n唔嚟元朗 以後唔駛旨意屯元天人出港島"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:14:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff49d09164395722b6e196ea96a9757392c029e","tid":1352453,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:15:21.000Z","msg":"撞"},{"pid":"0efdc3b236a6ee50f38ed242d3a7cdd421c3f249","tid":1352453,"uid":196430,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:16:41.000Z","msg":"去元朗唔係打交，而係宣示香港嘅主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19735d322fef758649aeba0d2ee763a1c85e6761","tid":1352453,"uid":254523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:18:14.000Z","msg":"入黎研究727裝備<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n一齊研究"},{"pid":"a8d0179ff4ff6fcadeb74de9b78c77df76b3eb55","tid":1352453,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:18:32.000Z","msg":"【HKSDF】香港自衛隊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dowzBT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dowzBT</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思阻阻你<br />\n為大家安全麻煩入嚟討論下"},{"pid":"79149a73fd8473d31531c270659c67c630b18e94","tid":1352453,"uid":86253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:19:29.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073caa58f11a6accb37e6b1d1f4e0be4a384476f","tid":1352453,"uid":196430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:19:37.000Z","msg":"怯，你就輸一世"},{"pid":"449975d3bf9a6805cc4d108b30576a40a4d8d982","tid":1352453,"uid":273319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0efdc3b236a6ee50f38ed242d3a7cdd421c3f249","tid":1352453,"uid":196430,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:16:41.000Z","msg":"去元朗唔係打交，而係宣示香港嘅主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:19:53.000Z","msg":"點醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185cd1f30e5cd11039ac7b0391a47be36e539924","tid":1352453,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:20:02.000Z","msg":"話唔應該光復元朗既入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PRk5ct.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PRk5ct.png&h=44b28edb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8E3ixt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8E3ixt.png&h=ad20a7e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EnGJixu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEnGJixu.png&h=eb093d23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEWAT5Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEWAT5Q.png&h=6acd11d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31f8f89ae01f2f64e36370bec4151f8c3df7457d","tid":1352453,"uid":180429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:20:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持前線理念同決定</span>"},{"pid":"f2d86a6081c3464de4bb86f63d6b9869fbdeb0db","tid":1352453,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0407b929acdbb61281abdbe8135557bc0fea444f","tid":1352453,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:25:49.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"06f057d792ef4e8c92ca8f6d361981d87aa16818","tid":1352453,"uid":196430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:27:13.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無睇過岩井俊二嘅《青春電幻物語》，入面有一段，係講伊滕步畀人校園欺凌，甚至強姦，但佢喺畀人強姦嘅第二日，刻意剃光頭，大搖大擺嘅如常返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢就係要話所有強權聽，你侵犯到我嘅身體，但打擊唔到我嘅意志同靈魂，從此學校入面，無人敢再蝦佢<br />\n<br />\n香港而家係一樣，我地去元朗，唔係為咗打交同尋仇，而係話畀所有人同路人同歒人聽，香港仲係屬於香港人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1be042f80dd92f44fffdba2817eb78023ec0630","tid":1352453,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:28:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cdbbf4b23c0c0fb11e970f3c3c730e305c5edc7","tid":1352453,"uid":205566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:29:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8403d8329c15e570e09038ddb082a196814501","tid":1352453,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:29:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352329\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352329</a><br />\n<br />\n唔去以後和理非唔使出黎"},{"pid":"35652024c54398bc7fa38f2c92e30d1b6ea35091","tid":1352453,"uid":49994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:29:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a0d56421794aa047bb6732024f96cc073237b23","tid":1352453,"uid":180429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:30:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持前線理念同決定</span>"},{"pid":"1ceb4da6507a7f4d81ebbc245be7bbea6dcf6eeb","tid":1352453,"uid":9078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:30:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打唔打都係其次，你班友咪再spin我地送頭。咁樣講次次出黎行都有人&lsquo;送頭&rsquo;啦</span>"},{"pid":"9942540afcfd307c71947b10e834232d2311828a","tid":1352453,"uid":192754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:30:20.000Z","msg":"有冇人申請不反對通知書？<br />\n有先夠人"},{"pid":"9f7dca5f3774ca63c480320dc1ab6b573483fc4e","tid":1352453,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:31:26.000Z","msg":"失無撚風向撚收皮啦<br />\n冇人唔記得36槍爆頭<br />\n我地依家做咩都聚焦政權"},{"pid":"8c4559ddd524475b7cb4ef3c6aec5707077cc84f","tid":1352453,"uid":264792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T19:32:42.000Z","msg":"光復元朗以前搞過啦，送咩頭啊？"}]}